downloadDescription: System Center Operations Manager management pack for Exchange connector and Intune
detailsSection: The System Center Operations Manager (SCOM) management pack for Exchange connector can help you parse the Exchange connector logs. This gives you different ways of monitoring the service when you need to troubleshoot issues.
systemRequirementsSection: The Exchange Connector SCOM Pack for Operations Manager is designed for the following versions of System Center Operations Manager: • System Center Operations Manager 2007 R2 • System Center Operations Manager 2012 • System Center Operations Manager 2012 SP1 • System Center Operations Manager 2012 R2
installInstructionSection: See here for instructions on importing System Center Operations Manager packs: https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/hh212691(v=sc.12).aspx
